        "title": "How to add a rule to CheckStyle.xml",
        "body": "<p>How to add a rule to CheckStyle.xml (IDEA) which will mark as an error the use of certain characters, for example: [ ]<\/p>\n",
        "question_id": 49883490,
        "tags": [
            "java",
            "intellij-idea",
